{"type": "article", "id": 23870, "title": "双面镜切割灯和弯曲凳", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155814Ml3DriXthdvoCqb7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏灯有行星绕着轨道旋转的感觉，一个双面圆镜将手工吹制而成的玻璃球面倾斜切开，也将光线一分为二，但因为镜面反射，光线仍然是发散出来的，并没有被遮挡。而倾斜切割的镜面给人一种摇摆和失重的瞬间。除此之外，他们设计了一个有些微微弯曲的凳子，似乎有很多人已经坐过了，给人一种亲近感。HCWD Studio（ 炘工作室）在纽约，由两位华裔设计师组成，<a href=\"http://www.hcwangdesign.com/blog/\">这里是工作室链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615581290GTmRxb8Li7zoCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155813T1MFQtZhj9EiKvA7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155813so3r8TVw4EivCYUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64270833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155813FIJNXWqbkGT9zE4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155814OQ27GIt6NWeK3FyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}